<p>I am trying to upload file using ajax in codeigniter framework. But i got error message 'You did not select a file to upload.' Please check this code</p>  <p>View</p>  <pre><code>&lt;form method="POST" action="" enctype="multipart/form-data" id="file_upload"&gt; &lt;input type="file" id="file-input" name="file"&gt; &lt;/form&gt; </code></pre>  <p>JQuery</p>  <pre><code>$("#file-input").change(function() {     var formData = new FormData($('#file_upload')[0]);         $.ajax({         url : 'do_upload',         data: formData,         type:'POST',         mimeType: "multipart/form-data",         cache: false,         contentType: false,         processData: false,         //  dataType:'json',         success:function(data){             alert(data);         }     }); }); </code></pre>  <p>controller</p>  <pre><code>public  function do_upload(){     $config['upload_path'] = './uploads/';     $config['allowed_types'] = 'gif|jpg|png';     $config['max_size'] = '100';     $config['max_width']  = '1024';     $config['max_height']  = '768';      $this-&gt;load-&gt;library('upload', $config);      if ( ! $this-&gt;upload-&gt;do_upload('file'))     {         echo  $this-&gt;upload-&gt;display_errors() ;      }     else     {         echo "Uploaded";     } } </code></pre>